    <p>Hyaluronic acid serums and moisturizers are essential in the Italian climate, where dry air depletes skin hydration rapidly. Products containing hyaluronic acid cost €8-18 and are available at every farmacia. These serums are applied to damp skin before moisturizer to maximize hydration - a simple step many expats find transformative for their skin health.</p>
