    <p>Psoriasis and eczema treatments are partially available over-the-counter (moisturizing creams, gentle cleansers) at farmacie for €10-20, with stronger prescription treatments (topical corticosteroids, tacrolimus) requiring dermatologist evaluation. The SSN covers most prescription dermatitis treatments fully, making specialized care accessible.</p>

