    metaDescription: "Complete guide to Italian vaccination schedule for expats. Learn required vaccines, SSN registration, and healthcare requirements in Italy.",
    keywords: ["Italian vaccination schedule", "expat vaccinations Italy", "SSN registration vaccines", "Italian health requirements", "childhood vaccines Italy", "vaccination calendar Italy"],
