    tldr: "Knowing Italian emergency numbers can be lifesaving in urgent situations. The 112 number covers all emergencies, but understanding other numbers like 118 for ambulance and 115 for fire helps expats respond appropriately.",
    metaDescription: "Essential Italian emergency numbers for expats. Learn when to call 112, 118, 115, and other emergency services in Italy.",
    keywords: ["Italian emergency numbers", "112 Italy emergency", "118 ambulance Italy", "emergency services Italy", "expat emergency guide", "pronto soccorso emergency"],
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591695821749-5a66e3eea6a3?w=1200",
