    metaDescription: "Guide to Italian emergency rooms (pronto soccorso). Learn procedures, triage systems, and what to expect during emergency visits.",
    keywords: ["pronto soccorso Italy", "Italian emergency room", "hospital emergency procedure", "triage system Italy", "emergency room costs Italy", "healthcare emergency guide"],
